QuestData.Title: Package Recovery
QuestData.Description: You take the package and confirm that indeed it comes from Magistrix Erona. Alarion would probably want you to bring it to her.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Outrunner Alarion with Erona's Package.
QuestData.RewardText: By the Sunwell! That's the third outrunner we've lost this month.$B$BI appreciate your courage in venturing into Dawning Street. The guards need to keep a closer eye on these blasted Wretched.
